{\an1}Brandon, maybe this
<i>has</i> gone too far.

39:42.922 --> 39:44.632
{\an1}Maybe you should just
tell everybody to go home.

39:44.715 --> 39:47.134
{\an3}Dad, come on, you
sound like Spiro Agnew.

39:47.218 --> 39:49.095
Everybody, come on,
we're going in!

